@startuml stm_primary
title <<stm>> CMainFrame (VSIM_OGL) Primary State Machine

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor<<browse>>   #e3f2fd
    BorderColor<<browse>>       #1565c0
    FontColor<<browse>>         #0d47a1
    BackgroundColor<<terminal>> #e8f5e9
    BorderColor<<terminal>>     #2e7d32
    FontColor<<terminal>>       #1b5e20
}
skinparam shadowing false
top to bottom direction

state "pre_create" as PreCreate <<browse>>
state "created" as Created <<browse>>
state "closing" as Closing <<browse>>
state "closed" as Closed <<terminal>>

PreCreate --> PreCreate : pre_create_window
PreCreate -down-> Created : on_create
Created --> Created : on_bar_check(toolbar)\non_bar_check(beam_param_bar)\non_bar_check(explorer_bar)\non_bar_check(status_bar)\non_update_control_bar_menu(_)
Created -down-> Closing : on_close
Closing -down-> Closed  : destruct

note right of Created
    Four docking control bars created.
    OnBarCheck/OnUpdateControlBarMenu
    handle their visibility toggles
    via the framework defaults; no
    overrides in this class.
end note

@enduml
